        },
        {
          "title": "[ ] Use a stateless password management solution - <a href=\"http://masterpasswordapp.com/\">Master Password</a>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "topic": "Block advertising",
      "items": [
        {
          "title": "[ ] Set unified hosts file to block fakenews, gambling, porn, social, adware &amp; malware - <a href=\"https://github.com/StevenBlack/hosts\">hosts</a>"
        },
